msgid "If your only keyboard or mouse *are* connected through a USB qube, and that USB qube *is* a disposable, then you will have to enter a special command that shuts down all of your qubes, switches the USB qube’s disposable template to the new template, then starts the USB qube again. In order to avoid being locked out of your system, you must be very careful to enter this command without typos and with the correct substitutions."
